Sentencas: This research has been conducted on BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.2-xAxO3-delta, which is doped by different metal elements of Zr, Mg, and Zn.
Titulo: Tailoring the oxygen permeability of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.2-x AxO3-? (x=0, 0.1; A: Zr, Mg, Zn) cubic perovskite

Sentencas: The prime concern of this study is to observe the oxygen permeability, corresponding to mixed ionicelectronic conductivities of the prepared samples.
Titulo: Tailoring the oxygen permeability of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.2-x AxO3-? (x=0, 0.1; A: Zr, Mg, Zn) cubic perovskite

Sentencas: Synchrotron x-ray powder diffraction explorations confirmed that all prepared compositions belong to the perovskite structure with impurity-free cubic phase.
Titulo: Tailoring the oxygen permeability of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.2-x AxO3-? (x=0, 0.1; A: Zr, Mg, Zn) cubic perovskite

Sentencas: All the samples express thermal stability.
Titulo: Tailoring the oxygen permeability of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.2-x AxO3-? (x=0, 0.1; A: Zr, Mg, Zn) cubic perovskite

Sentencas: The raising of total conductivity of all the studied compositions shows relative relation to the change of temperature, where doped samples have higher values than undoped ones.
Titulo: Tailoring the oxygen permeability of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.2-x AxO3-? (x=0, 0.1; A: Zr, Mg, Zn) cubic perovskite

Sentencas: This study found that Mg and Zn doping improve oxygen permeability in comparison to BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.1Zr0.1O3-delta (BCFZY) because of the higher oxygen non-stoichiometry in addition to the low average binding energy.
Titulo: Tailoring the oxygen permeability of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.2-x AxO3-? (x=0, 0.1; A: Zr, Mg, Zn) cubic perovskite

Sentencas: The high oxygen permeability of Mg and Zn doped samples indicates potentiality as a cathode of solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Tailoring the oxygen permeability of BaCo0.4Fe0.4Y0.2-x AxO3-? (x=0, 0.1; A: Zr, Mg, Zn) cubic perovskite
